EBS:- elastic block service
ebs is a block level storage service
provided by aws.amazon.com for use with ec2 instance
it provide presistent storage , meaning your data remains safe even if the ec2 instance is stopped
ebs allows to create a storage volume & attach them ec2 instance
in simple term it a storage of ec2 instance
system srorage for amazon ec2 vms

USES OF EBS:- 
      1) storing appliocation data 
      2) databse store
      3) backup and recovry
      4) server file system
